OL,3,CWhat you need to know as Pakistan
OL,4,Cdeclares 'open war' with Afghanistan
OL,6,FPakistan has declared an "open war"
OL,7,Fwith Afghanistan after launching what
OL,8,Fit described as retaliatory strikes
OL,9,Fagainst its neighbour, further ramping
OL,10,Fup tensions between the two Middle
OL,11,FEastern countries.
OL,13,FFighting between the two countries
OL,14,Fescalated into a serious armed
OL,15,Fconfrontation before reaching an
OL,16,Funeasy ceasefire back in October.
OL,18,FThe two countries share a long and
OL,19,Fcomplicated history, dating back to
OL,20,FPakistan's creation in 1947.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
