OL,3,CWhat you need to know as Pakistan
OL,4,Cdeclares 'open war' with Afghanistan
OL,6,FBound by social, ethnic, and economic
OL,7,Fties, relations have been volatile and
OL,8,Fat times descended into armed conflict.
OL,10,FAfter the Afghan strikes, Pakistan's
OL,11,FDefence Minister Khawaja Mohammad Asif
OL,12,Fsaid in a post on X: "Our patience has
OL,13,Fnow run out. Now it is open war
OL,14,Fbetween us."
OL,16,FHere, ITV News breaks down the latest
OL,17,Fescalation between the two countries
OL,18,Fand why they are fighting in the first
OL,19,Fplace.
OL,21,FBackground to the latest conflict
OL,26,@tD@VOUvD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
