OL,3,CWhat you need to know as Pakistan
OL,4,Cdeclares 'open war' with Afghanistan
OL,6,FAfghanistan launched an extensive
OL,7,Fcross-border attack into Pakistan
OL,8,Falong six provinces on Thursday night,
OL,9,Fin what it said was retaliation for
OL,10,Fopposing airstrikes on Sunday.
OL,12,FPakistan had said those airstrikes had
OL,13,Ftargeted and killed dozens of
OL,14,Fmilitants in Afghanistan, but Kabul
OL,15,Fsaid only civilians, including women
OL,16,Fand children, had been killed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
