OL,3,CWhat you need to know as Pakistan
OL,4,Cdeclares 'open war' with Afghanistan
OL,6,FIn response, Pakistan carried out
OL,7,Fairstrikes in the early hours of
OL,8,FFriday on the Afghan capital and two
OL,9,Fother areas, Kandahar and Paktia. The
OL,10,Fborder fighting, which had ceased by
OL,11,Fthen, restarted and was continuing on
OL,12,FFriday.
OL,14,FPakistan has witnessed a sharp rise in
OL,15,Fmilitant violence within the country
OL,16,Fin recent years, including suicide
OL,17,Fbombings and coordinated assaults
OL,18,Ftargeting security forces.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
