OL,3,CWhat you need to know as Pakistan
OL,4,Cdeclares 'open war' with Afghanistan
OL,6,FPakistani authorities blame the
OL,7,FPakistani Taliban, known as Tehrik-e-
OL,8,FTaliban Pakistan, or TTP, for many of
OL,9,Fthe attacks, and accuse Afghanistan of
OL,10,Fproviding a safe haven for the group
OL,11,Finside Afghanistan.
OL,13,FKabul rejects the allegations and says
OL,14,Fit does not allow anyone to use Afghan
OL,15,Fsoil for attacks on any country,
OL,16,Fincluding Pakistan.
OL,18,FThe Pakistani Taliban
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
