OL,3,CWhat you need to know as Pakistan
OL,4,Cdeclares 'open war' with Afghanistan
OL,6,FCreated in 2007, the TTP brought
OL,7,Ftogether different outlawed groups
OL,8,Fthat agreed to work together against
OL,9,FPakistan and support the Afghan
OL,10,FTaliban, who at the time were fighting
OL,11,FUS and NATO forces.
OL,13,FThe United Nations and the United
OL,14,FStates have designated it a terrorist
OL,15,Forganisation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
