OL,3,CWhat you need to know as Pakistan
OL,4,Cdeclares 'open war' with Afghanistan
OL,6,FThe group seeks stricter enforcement
OL,7,Fof Islamic laws, the release of its
OL,8,Fmembers imprisoned in Pakistan, and a
OL,9,Freduction in Pakistani military
OL,10,Fpresence in parts of Khyber
OL,11,FPakhtunkhwa, the province bordering
OL,12,FAfghanistan that it has long used as a
OL,13,Fbase.
OL,15,FAlthough separate, the group is
OL,16,Fclosely allied with the Afghan
OL,17,FTaliban, which now runs Afghanistan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
