OL,3,CWhat you need to know as Pakistan
OL,4,Cdeclares 'open war' with Afghanistan
OL,6,FMany of its leaders and fighters are
OL,7,Fbelieved to have taken refuge in
OL,8,FAfghanistan since the Taliban's return
OL,9,Fto power in 2021, further straining
OL,10,Fties.
OL,12,FIn 2022, Afghanistan brokered a short-
OL,13,Flived ceasefire between the TTP and
OL,14,FPakistan. The truce collapsed when the
OL,15,FTTP accused Pakistan's military of
OL,16,Fviolating the agreement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
