OL,3,CWhat you need to know as Pakistan
OL,4,Cdeclares 'open war' with Afghanistan
OL,6,FPakistan was one of only three
OL,7,Fcountries - along with Saudi Arabia
OL,8,Fand the United Arab Emirates - to
OL,9,Frecognise the first Taliban government
OL,10,Fafter it first seized power in 1996.
OL,12,FHowever, after the September 11, 2001,
OL,13,Fattacks in the United States,
OL,14,FIslamabad aligned itself with
OL,15,FWashington in the US-led war in
OL,16,FAfghanistan, a shift that angered
OL,17,FIslamist militant groups at home.
OL,19,FConflict at the border
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
