OL,3,CWhat you need to know as Pakistan
OL,4,Cdeclares 'open war' with Afghanistan
OL,6,FMuch of the tension is concentrated
OL,7,Falong the two countries' 2,611-
OL,8,Fkilometre (1,622-mile) frontier known
OL,9,Fas the Durand Line.
OL,11,FNamed after British diplomat Mortimer
OL,12,FDurand and established in 1893, the
OL,13,Fline cuts through the heartland of the
OL,14,Ftribal areas of the Pashtun,
OL,15,FAfghanistan's largest ethnic group and
OL,16,Falso the group from which the Afghan
OL,17,FTaliban stem.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772309090
OL,3,CWhat you need to know as Pakistan
OL,4,Cdeclares 'open war' with Afghanistan
OL,6,FAlthough the line is internationally
OL,7,Frecognised as Pakistan's western
OL,8,Fborder, Afghanistan does not recognise
OL,9,Fit as such.
OL,11,FBoth countries often accuse each other
OL,12,Fof turning a blind eye to Islamic
OL,13,Fmilitants operating along it.
OL,15,FSimmering tensions
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
