OL,3,CWhat you need to know as Pakistan
OL,4,Cdeclares 'open war' with Afghanistan
OL,6,FTension between Afghanistan and
OL,7,FPakistan has been high for months. It
OL,8,Freached a peak last year when dozens
OL,9,Fof civilians, security forces and
OL,10,Fmilitants were killed in the deadliest
OL,11,Fclashes between the countries in years.
OL,13,FOn October 8, militants ambushed an
OL,14,Farmy convoy in Pakistan's Orakzai
OL,15,Fdistrict, killing 11 soldiers. The
OL,16,Fassault was part of a broader wave of
OL,17,Fviolence that has killed hundreds of
OL,18,Fcivilians and security personnel in
OL,19,Frecent years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772309090
OL,3,CWhat you need to know as Pakistan
OL,4,Cdeclares 'open war' with Afghanistan
OL,6,FPrime Minister Shehbaz Sharif said
OL,7,FPakistan could no longer tolerate the
OL,8,Fcontinued loss of life and announced
OL,9,Fthe military had been granted full
OL,10,Fauthority to respond. The following
OL,11,Fday, Pakistan's military carried out
OL,12,Fstrikes inside Afghanistan, prompting
OL,13,Fcross-border clashes.
OL,15,FA Qatari-mediated ceasefire in mid-
OL,16,FOctober ended the fighting, although
OL,17,Fsince then there have been repeated
OL,18,Fstrikes and skirmishes in the frontier
OL,19,Farea, leading to dozens of deaths. The
OL,20,Ftwo sides differ widely on the
OL,21,Fcasualty figures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772309090
OL,3,CWhat you need to know as Pakistan
OL,4,Cdeclares 'open war' with Afghanistan
OL,6,FPeace talks held in Istanbul in
OL,7,FNovember failed to reach a long-term
OL,8,Fsolution.
OL,10,FAfghan refugee deportations
OL,12,FTension has also escalated over
OL,13,FPakistan's mass deportation of Afghan
OL,14,Frefugees.
OL,16,FIn 2023, Pakistan launched a
OL,17,Fnationwide crackdown on foreigners
OL,18,Fliving there without legal status.
OL,19,FWhile officials said the campaign was
OL,20,Fnot aimed at any single nationality,
OL,21,Fit has primarily affected Afghans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
