PN,31615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772309090
OL,3,CWhat you need to know as Pakistan
OL,4,Cdeclares 'open war' with Afghanistan
OL,6,FOver the past four decades, millions
OL,7,Fof Afghans have sought refuge in
OL,8,FPakistan, fleeing war, political
OL,9,Finstability and economic hardship in
OL,10,Ftheir homeland.
OL,12,FThe crackdown is affecting more than
OL,13,Ftwo million Afghans in Pakistan,
OL,14,Fincluding some who were born there.
OL,16,FIran, Afghanistan's western neighbour,
OL,17,Fhas also carried out expulsions,
OL,18,Ffurther straining resources in
OL,19,Fimpoverished Afghanistan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772309090
OL,3,CWhat you need to know as Pakistan
OL,4,Cdeclares 'open war' with Afghanistan
OL,6,FThe UN's refugee agency says a total
OL,7,Fof 5.4 million people have returned to
OL,8,Fthe country since October 2023, mostly
OL,9,Ffrom Pakistan and Iran.
OL,11,FInternational alarm
OL,13,FThe fighting has alarmed the
OL,14,Finternational community, particularly
OL,15,Fas the area is one where other
OL,16,Fmilitant groups, including al-Qaida
OL,17,Fand the Islamic State group, still
OL,18,Fhave a presence and have been trying
OL,19,Fto resurface.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
