OL,3,CWhat you need to know as Pakistan
OL,4,Cdeclares 'open war' with Afghanistan
OL,6,FIn October, Turkey, Qatar and Saudi
OL,7,FArabia had facilitated talks between
OL,8,Fthe sides.
OL,10,FAt the time, US President Donald Trump
OL,11,Fhad also weighed in, saying he
OL,12,Fintended to resolve the conflict "very
OL,13,Fquickly." Whether he will do so again
OL,14,Fremains to be seen.
OL,16,FTurkish Foreign Minister Hakan Fidan
OL,17,Fspoke with his Pakistani, Afghan,
OL,18,FQatari and Saudi counterparts, a
OL,19,FTurkish official said Friday, speaking
OL,20,Fon condition of anonymity in line with
OL,21,Fgovernment policy.
