OL,3,CWhat you need to know as Pakistan
OL,4,Cdeclares 'open war' with Afghanistan
OL,6,FRussia has called for an immediate
OL,7,Fhalt to the fighting and for a
OL,8,Fdiplomatic resolution to the conflict,
OL,9,Fwhile Iran said it was ready to assist
OL,10,Fin facilitating dialogue.
OL,12,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,13,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,14,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,15,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/18
